Title : List of books about food and drink
Text : This is a '''list of books about food and drink'''.<ref>[https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/books/10589148/The-10-best-food-and-drink-books-of-all-time.html The 10 best food and drink books]</ref> Not all of the books listed here are [[Cookbook|Cookbooks]], yet the content would be pertaining to food and drink.<ref>[http://greatist.com/health/best-cookbooks The 22 Best Cookbooks of 2013]</ref><ref>[https://www.buzzfeed.com/emofly/best-cookbooks-to-cook-your-way-through 19 Cookbooks that will improve your life]</ref>

